{"tid":27427,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[ F F ] 喪屍來襲救地球","createTime":"2016-12-07T10:17:14.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-07T10:22:23.000Z","uid":46312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c3809a81b807804e6e2e7bf61eb9dcca21479a97","tid":27427,"uid":46312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T10:17:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: green;\">一人一個/幾個可以殺屍武器<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n假設香港變曬死城<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n全部人都要搵地方躲藏<br />\n依家可以擁有一把主要武器旁身<br />\n可以同喪屍搏鬥之餘<br />\n仲可以守護自己地頭<br />\n解釋埋點解要揀呢樣武器<br />\n<br />\n下面我會講下點解我要揀呢d武器<br />\n同埋有咩武器我唔會揀<br />\n<br />\n本人首選一定係鈍器<br />\n1. 鈍器可以重複使用<br />\n2. 損耗冇咁大 例如崩裂/利器變鈍<br />\n3. 冇咁容易卡住係肉體出唔返黎<br />\n4. 啪落去聲音畫面感覺好爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n5. 鈍器通常有一定重量可以借力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">心儀武器<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\na. 棒球棍<img src=\"http://clps10160805.weebly.com/uploads/1/3/5/2/13527261/8523781_orig.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fclps10160805.weebly.com%2Fuploads%2F1%2F3%2F5%2F2%2F13527261%2F8523781_orig.jpg&h=a420475c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n棒球棍設計方便用力同揮動<br />\n對於速度上有一定既優勢<br />\n根據專科醫生表示 要打爆頭骨必須要用超過<span style=\"color: orange;\">一百磅力度</span><br />\n相等於中量級拳手蓄勢發出的拳力<br />\n估計全力揮棒都接近一百磅<br />\n喪屍必爆頭無疑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nb.武士刀<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.rghknives.com.tw/images/Taiwan/twn_sc-16_enl.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.rghknives.com.tw%2Fimages%2FTaiwan%2Ftwn_sc-16_enl.jpg&h=1fcd2c24&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n雖然利器損耗大<br />\n但係作為喪屍主題愛好者<br />\n難免會對武士刀有愛<br />\n根據同一位醫生說明<br />\n「頭骨硬既程度一般尖刀絕不能刺入腦中<br />\n一般尖銳性物件企圖刺入頭骨，只會被其渾圓的形狀跣開」<br />\n但係打開喪屍game同睇開喪屍片既我<br />\n有理由相信對住頸部直接橫刀一片<br />\n一定可以屍頭落地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔會考慮<br />\na. 手槍<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/d/d7/Smith_%26_Wesson_M%26P.jpg/450px-Smith_%26_Wesson_M%26P.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2Fthumb%2Fd%2Fd7%2FSmith_%2526_Wesson_M%2526P.jpg%2F450px-Smith_%2526_Wesson_M%2526P.jpg&h=8d606d72&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一般左輪手槍都係射得6發<br />\n射得黎仲要上彈<br />\n平時又要練習準繩<br />\n消耗量仲多過d食物<br />\n<br />\nb. 斧頭<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.dbqx.com.cn/family/UploadFiles_7470/200911/2009112409412473.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.dbqx.com.cn%2Ffamily%2FUploadFiles_7470%2F200911%2F2009112409412473.jpg&h=cafc606d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n基於斧頭太墜手<br />\n而且容易卡住係肉入面<br />\n萬一一對二果陣抽唔返出黎就係咁先<br />\n<br />\n暫時得咁多 諗到再加<br />\n<br />\nP.S.<br />\n*武器必須要係現實存在既<br />\n*武器必須係未經組合 e.g. 手槍, 生果刀, 垃圾桶等等 <br />\n  組合過果d就唔可以 e.g. 鐵絲棒球棍, 電話禁極刀, 電擊拳套等等<br />\n*必須係可用拎上手 e.g. x坦克, 衛星炮, 核彈<br />\n*喪屍爆頭必死+唔會變身<br />\n*被咬先會傳染 但掂到血唔會傳染<br />\n<br />\nReference:頭條日報<a href=\"http://news.stheadline.com/dailynews/content_hk/2011/10/17/165072.asp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.stheadline.com%2Fdailynews%2Fcontent_hk%2F2011%2F10%2F17%2F165072.asp&d=lWdkQpLmCgxSW1DATsQyGaEBD16zEvtm8%2BkmVdQ%2BVC0%3D&h=0e2f36b3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.stheadline.com%2Fdailynews%2Fcontent_hk%2F2011%2F10%2F17%2F165072.asp&h=3e858165\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.stheadline.com/dailynews/content_hk/2011/10/17/165072.asp</a>"},{"pid":"f1f288845ac77ef8feb9e9ce76c0cf932d3f176c","tid":27427,"uid":10338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T10:22:23.000Z","msg":"摺凳"}]}